{"h27575e3eg5076g4ee0g9663g7470076c02b5": ["Not exactly a fair fight, was it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h1a6a4c15gf7d9g4b31g90d2gf1f0ba9f2277": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "hcf06ab0bg8d20g47a1g92f8gbd86c45455fc": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h696f988eg8d16g4512g9775g07d148e696ce": ["Ha! The tieflings have teeth after all.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h9577620dgfc2eg44b0gb191g6a70a8c45401": ["One pest among many, hardly to be missed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h8b75c691g665fg4f41ga38eg8ec95adfb8ca": ["  | I never took you for a murderer. That goblin didn't deserve to die like that. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h9b49eb19g315fg47cfg80c3ga8824596493f": ["Hardly a winning display of archery, but it did the job.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h6a277df7g7ac5g4386g8f7bgde267d0c3af1": ["  | I never took you for a murderer. That goblin didn't deserve to die like that. (Gale Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h91547359g272dg48fag8b35g427d367b4cb9": ["I know she was a goblin, but killing someone defenceless in a cage...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "0a7c65c9-dcc7-8cf2-4362-7c025eb784b1"], "h2262ea3fg6103g47f6gb43bg4fc8d9f7c67e": ["Nice - she saved the work of having to do it ourselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h3db2ec5agc3c7g440dgbee5ge75a05a103d4": ["A commendable choice. The horde must be thinned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h960bfb23g99b4g41a7g89edgec5982c015e0": ["I'm glad someone's willing to exterminate pests.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h9ffb51c5ge6c0g4e48gadf0g93e136ef3049": ["Goblins are dangerous pests. The more that're turned into worm fodder, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h819ca849g6c6cg4b1fgb736gbeea9e658e3c": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h72902b13g053cg497eg83f9gb741f494cdc4": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h79fa256bg09fdg41e0g8e86g02664d0fc6a3": ["| I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h863c4060g54fbg4e63ga312gfe5530f77e2e": ["| I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h59354cd2g084bg4fe2g93a4g1ddc0afb8e17": ["She'd have done the same to us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "7ec3a6cb-e881-fbea-fb3e-29f53a20c9d7"], "h48b0df72g7472g4bd3ga81eg027891c1ce4f": ["Right - she saved the work of having to do it ourselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "ha757646agb683g4406g84fdg43515c2af360": ["A commendable choice indeed. The horde must be thinned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h379946e1gd9a7g48f4g9cc3gdcda1bc26e8f": ["Just so. And I'm glad someone's willing to exterminate the pests.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h52fef896g7652g4d40g81cag0c720b48443b": ["Indeed. Goblins are dangerous pests. The more that're turned into worm fodder, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "hbc7922b0gaf7fg4f6ega37dg8980c9a3cd03": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h16431114g7568g4756gaa09g966d8a1bfb3d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h25dd006dg3516g4997ga7f4g4eb2a4ee5331": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h9cfac8d1g051bg4b68g8a64g69ff4d68e308": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h17eb110egbf40g483bgbf87g31d4866f6202": ["Exactly. What's another dead goblin in the scheme of things?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "d85b0856-f65d-1988-de1c-93fe48d4c517"], "h20c4530dg2841g4042gb083gaff2b6b686f0": ["Right - she saved the work of having to do it ourselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "h8c05bc7eg962ag4eeeg91fegf8433fa7334a": ["A commendable choice indeed. The horde must be thinned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "hdec4bc2cg964eg457egab3cg2929edb3abaa": ["Just so. And I'm glad someone's willing to exterminate the pests.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "hc2b1bcd3g1f45g442ag91e0g95d899bff38f": ["Indeed. Goblins are dangerous pests. The more that're turned into worm fodder, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "h3c0a6ddfgaebeg4745g8db9gdcbab29360f1": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "h0b9856e1g599eg4529g9585gd90dc41e47bf": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "h6ff1939cg9dc6g464bgb663gb5cea2158196": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "h262839bcgb51dg4a65g95a5gad365841aae9": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "hbb262861g0a41g4eeegad8cg87b14da58e36": ["That goblin would have killed Kanon just the same. I don't blame Arka for taking matters into her own hands.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "92006323-877f-a9af-4073-8b04b2fd5dde"], "hd874666egdf6cg409bgbd09g23cf51e63a61": ["Right - she saved the work of having to do it ourselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h3edd6989gb713g4723g979dg1839a8186acd": ["A commendable choice indeed. The horde must be thinned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "hd1a7bfdcg2901g4c91ga173ge3f76c03ec6c": ["Just so. And I'm glad someone's willing to exterminate the pests.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h138973e1g3d84g47e7g97ebgac11d868ca73": ["Indeed. Goblins are dangerous pests. The more that're turned into worm fodder, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h262c1869gf2e1g460cg809age4a5b07e002a": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h97bed329g4c38g420egb776gb555727ec936": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h25f3b03ag8e2bg40bcg81dcg48c5d000d919": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h91640a0ag13c6g4c8eg8a9cgc95dca61c830": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h9da0c7e6gb35eg4c3ega315gd0e398f4e0fc": ["In my book, our hands are clean. Let dead goblins lie.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "f71cae0d-22ce-2b8e-faa6-b5d70c64f33f"], "h4fdb1e30g8cfdg4817g995eg6189dad2b365": ["Either way, it was only a goblin. No reason to wring our hands over this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "hb9b313fagea6bg439eg8bffg6a5e374177fa": ["She's dead. Let it be.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "he7b5b3e2g0828g484bga2a9g9d7e401d00bb": ["It's just a goblin. We don't have to go on about it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "hf1e54317gc94eg414ega334gd18bc6df7034": ["No point in dwelling on it, in either case.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "h47cc327bg1758g4f31ga4dfg44e6560a6f88": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "h1ca75fceg4623g452dg976cg7c3e415b2594": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "h566957c1g4ce0g40dcg8c3cg260c157cfefd": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "h49d1b079gbb2bg4dfag9a6fg87a55c0d68ff": ["| Well we don't need to decide right now. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "h198f777fg120cg409dgb426ga3272c4a309c": ["I suppose she's dead either way. We can debate more later.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8aa8f108-5620-eaee-14d5-c9c448e6a4ee"], "hbb69bce1g3aa6g4b60gac18g0ec865fe4385": ["One down. Just a few thousand to go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "hbcb85c34g0f9dg4672gae28g2d7b03b72865": ["It is dead. We are better for it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "h3d98ba3dgbb3cg4998gb150gfe403bb8a51c": ["Here's to many more quarrels in many more goblins.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "ha11f9667g1bc0g4704gbcb4g13430d047af2": ["Nobody will shed any tears for a dead goblin. The opposite, more likely. Let's move on.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "hf8ae5218g945fg4859g812fge27f6c847212": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "h4b6d5356g6a41g47ddga5f1g106829e8fc8f": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "he4e0a721g9cccg46eag95adg98a137b25f67": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "h81c211e1g7065g4670ga1f7ga8928f973820": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "h6674c7d2g8ffdg48c9ga9a5g102745d263d2": ["Puts me in the mood to kill the rest of them, if I'm being honest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "be2e5ee5-4f87-69d5-b154-ca362cfc8646"], "hdadd5cc7gee1dg435agb16ag8d43ca06d4fb": ["It's always more fun when they put up a fight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "h472650e6g7929g4e19g9082gb03f6be130ed": ["Come - I tire of debate.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "hcf92f149g4eddg44a2gaba7g7184a773aac5": ["Not to worry. There are plenty more goblins.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "h2d91b24bg799ag4dadgba0dgaa971c46ca8c": ["The goblin's dead - there's nothing we can do now. Let's move on.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "hecf9e0f7gdca9g4d65g8b5fg022974750851": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "h0b6ea4b3geda4g4cfcg9394g6b1c281d9e02": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "hce9094b3ged8bg45f5ga575g98e06929977a": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "h7ee0342cgc11fg4190gbfccg96d1b8f5afe3": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "hde1b4b64g6afbg4e07ga911gc074cd3bc061": ["Let's leave her in peace. It's the least we can do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "1ccdf588-6901-9d73-7a02-06defb0faaab"], "h16b026edgcfdfg4c7fg9806gbdf1e2881c4e": ["I'd say she saved the work of having to do it ourselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "h76bd6906g0d9fg4c5fgba48gd7007fc565a0": ["It was a commendable choice. The horde must be thinned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "ha96d5819gda4ag42b8g8c6bg545976ee619e": ["Nonsense - I'm glad someone's exterminating the pests.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "hc3624ac2gf0a1g4ff1gb872g1fcf74ec9724": ["Please - goblins are dangerous pests. The more that're turned into worm fodder, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "h09a61658g8761g4eacgbf94g50178d85973e": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "h3ab204ecgf7d3g4585gad18ge15206ef3e9e": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "he34c4a12gdc07g4983g9be0g1e216956c0dc": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "h2bca666bg0b91g47e6g8d39g5ebc8ad749c7": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_RD_Shot.html", "8dbe36cd-def9-0554-05da-5f87044b9263"], "h070d629dg556ag4c48gbc6